From: OSMOSE Python repo (2026-04-17 deep-review fixes)
Subject: [PATCH] build: enable Java tests by default + document local Maven repo

Applies Tasks 13, 14, 15 from
osmose-python/docs/superpowers/plans/2026-04-17-codebase-review-fixes-plan.md
to the upstream osmose-master tree.

  - pom.xml: invert skipTests default so `mvn test` / `mvn verify` actually run tests.
  - .github/workflows/java-compile.yml: run `mvn -B verify` instead of
    `mvn -B package -DskipTests=true` so CI catches test regressions.
  - java/local/README.md: inventory the single vendored artifact
    (ml.options:options:1.0.0) and document the refresh procedure.

To apply against your osmose-master clone:

    cd <osmose-master clone>
    git apply path/to/osmose-master-java-fixes.patch

Or with plain `patch`:

    cd <osmose-master clone>
    patch -p1 < path/to/osmose-master-java-fixes.patch

